Prague transport company delivers chip card for the first time on Wednesday
On Wednesday, October 1, 2008, enter the history of the Prague Transport Company as the date when the first passenger to board the subways, trams and buses will have an electronic coupon in his pocket instead of a paper ticket.
The coupon is currently available to around 100,000 people who have an Opencard chip card.
Passengers can buy 30-day, 90-day and annual coupons (valid from 1 January 2009) and at the same time save on their chip card at the information centres and branches of the Transport Company at the Muzeum, M<0xC5><0xAF>stek, N<0xC3><0xA1>dra<0xC5><0xBE><0xC3><0xAD> Hole<0xC5><0xA1>ovice, And<0xC4><0x9B>l, Roztyly, Let<0xC5><0x88>any, Kabylisah, Rajska.
Coupons can already be purchased online from yesterday via the website of the Transport Company www.dpp.cz.
The service was used by more than 400 customers in the afternoon hours.
Those who start using internet commerce can finally forget about the renting windows of the metro stations, where they have had to stop regularly for long lines of tickets.
The coupon can be purchased online and stored on the Opencard card in one of the thirteen branches of the City Library.
"In these places, passengers will have a counter with trained servers who will help those interested to shop online and save their purchased coupons on their card," said Martin Opatrn<0xC3><0xBD>, project spokesman.
In addition to libraries, electronic coupons can be saved to Opencard in self-service vending machines installed in a few lobby areas.
What do these machines look like?
They are red, remind of ticket operators, and passengers may have noticed them at Roztyly, Bud<0xC4><0x9B>jovick<0xC3><0xA1>, I. P. Pavlova, Florenc and Vltavsk<0xC3><0xA1> metro stations.
"There are currently five of them in the city, but there should be 80 by the end of the year," Opatrn<0xC3><0xBD> added.
The ticket is automatically checked instead of the driver.
Managing vending machines that start operating tomorrow is simple.
Simply insert the Opencard chip card and the previously paid coupon will be saved automatically.
