The hopes of Düsseldorf depend on Frankfurt.
The letter from WestLB’s board of directors to the bank’s staff is not lacking in big words.
The merger of the units of the Düsseldorf financial institution and the Frankfurt Deca-Bank could create “the central capital market organisation of the savings bank financial group”, the letter reads.
