Meanwhile, the American geek culture and its savagery of enthusiastic computer fans, activists and users in many countries see the next generation of big companies, the "cool corporation," in contrast to its rival, Microsoft, who has been described as a world conqueror for Windows, no matter how much they both struggle for the same goal.
